+    before the 50-file bound tripped under Linux''s own directory-entry order. Fixed in both `os.walk()` call sites (`_find_manifest_paths()`''s
+    `_bounded_walk()`, `find_all_manifest_roots()`): `dirs[:] = sorted(...)`/`sorted(files)` makes the walk''s own effective
