+    — a genuinely different git ref than the existing per-`org_repo` lock (`LOCK_REF_PREFIX`, shared across every specialist''s
+    own `save_domain()`/`dispatch_gated_effect()` call), so no self-deadlock risk against that existing lock (confirmed: every
